org.osate.ge.di

Annotation Type ResolveReference


  • @Documented
 @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ResolveReference

    This annotation must not be applied to more than one method per class.

    Usages

    UsageDescriptionReturn Value
    Reference ResolverReturns the referenced business object. Returns null if the business object could not be returned.Object

    Named Parameters

    ParameterUsageDescription
    Names.REFERENCEReference ResolverThe reference for which to retrieve the business object.
    See Also:
    BuildReference
